data.description: This stunning home is nestled on a corner lot in the highly sought after neighborhood of Summers Corner. When you walk through the door, you are greeted with luxury vinyl plank floors and tall smooth ceilings. The home is flooded with natural light throughout. The open floor plan gives abundant space to entertain family and friends. The kitchen is a dream, featuring recessed lighting, dazzling granite countertops, new sleek stainless steel appliances, and a kitchen island, perfect for a breakfast bar. Upstairs, you will find the spacious master bedroom, complete with a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom featuring tile flooring, double vanity, and a glass enclosed walk-in shower. The home has a tankless water heater, so you can enjoy endless hot water.Step outside and enjoy the large fenced in backyard, great for grilling out and enjoying the nice weather with family and friends. This home is conveniently located a short 20 minute drive from Downtown Summerville, where you can find local shopping, dining and entertainment options while enjoying the feeling of a small town. Schedule a showing today!
